---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import HeaderEn from '../../components/HeaderEn.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_LAST_UPDATED_EN } from '../../consts';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Smart Advocacy | Miao He — Ontario Family Law Lawyer"
    description="Litigation experience is the strongest negotiating tool. Miao He negotiates when it makes sense and litigates when necessary — always putting your interests first. 647-930-6688."
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="Ontario family lawyer,litigation strategy,negotiation vs litigation,Miao He lawyer,Markham family law,Chinese family lawyer GTA" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Smart Advocacy | Miao He — Ontario Family Law Lawyer" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Litigation experience is the strongest negotiating tool. Miao He negotiates when it makes sense and litigates when necessary." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/og-image.jpg" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Smart Advocacy | Miao He — Ontario Family Law Lawyer",
    "description": "Litigation experience is the strongest negotiating tool. Miao He negotiates when it makes sense and litigates when necessary.",
    "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/smart-advocacy/",
    "isPartOf": {"@type": "WebSite", "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/"},
    "provider": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Miao He", "telephone": "647-930-6688"}
  }</script>
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/smart-advocacy/" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { background: #faf8f5; margin: 0; font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #2C1810; }
    .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C1810, #4A2C1A); padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2.5rem; }
    .page-hero .inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
    .page-hero h1 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); margin: 0 0 0.4rem; }
    .page-hero p { color: #D4A853; margin: 0; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .main-wrap { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E8E0D5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .card h2 { color: #7A5A1A; font-size: 1rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
    .card p { color: #5A4A3A; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .principle-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .principle-item { background: #F5EFE0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; }
    .principle-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .principle-title { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: #2C1810; }
    .cta-box { background: #F5EFE0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .cta-box h2 { color: #2C1810; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cta-box p { color: #5A4A3A; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #7A5A1A; color: #fff; padding: 0.7rem 1.8rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .principle-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <HeaderEn />
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> › Smart Advocacy</div>
      <h1>Smart Advocacy</h1>
      <p>Litigation experience is the strongest negotiating tool</p>
      <p class="page-last-updated page-last-updated--gradient">Page last updated: {SITE_LAST_UPDATED_EN}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="main-wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>THE PHILOSOPHY</h2>
      <p>Many people assume that hiring a litigator means going to court. The opposite is often true — the more experienced the litigator, the stronger the position at the negotiating table.</p>
      <p>Miao He's approach is simple: evaluate every case through a litigator's lens, pursue the best outcome whether that is through negotiation, mediation, or full trial — and never let emotion drive the strategy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>THREE PRINCIPLES</h2>
      <div class="principle-grid">
        <div class="principle-item">
          <div class="principle-icon">🤝</div>
          <div class="principle-title">Negotiate When It Makes Sense</div>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-item">
          <div class="principle-icon">⚖️</div>
          <div class="principle-title">Litigate When Necessary</div>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-item">
          <div class="principle-icon">🎯</div>
          <div class="principle-title">Always Protect Your Interests</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>WHY LITIGATION EXPERIENCE MATTERS IN NEGOTIATION</h2>
      <p>When the opposing party knows your lawyer has 15+ years of active court experience and 20+ court hours per month, negotiations shift. Credible litigation threat changes the dynamic at the table.</p>
      <p>A verified example: Yang v. Li, 2024 ONSC 4801 — eight simultaneous claims defeated at motion, costs awarded, appeal dismissed unanimously by three Divisional Court judges.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h2>Book a Consultation</h2>
      <p>30 minutes · $220 + HST · Mandarin & English</p>
      <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn">📞 647-930-6688</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</body>
</html>
